author: lhazlewood
msg: Moved configuration-related code to a new module.  This decouples configuration issues from Shiro's core API since config is largely environment specific (Ini, Tapestry, Spring, Guice, etc).  This also (finally) removes shiro-core's dependency on Apache Commons BeanUtils.
BeanUtils is now only a dependency if you're using Shiro's OGDL (Object Graph Definition Language-style configuration, like ini config.
Finally, some shared/common utility code was moved to shiro-lang.
